WEBVTT

00:18.760 --> 00:21.560
CHAPTER VI.

00:21.560 --> 00:25.040
Casting the Burden. Impressing the Subconscious.

00:26.340 --> 00:32.580
When man knows his own powers and the workings of his mind, his great desire is to find an easy

00:32.580 --> 00:39.040
and quick way to impress the subconscious with good, for simply an intellectual knowledge of

00:39.040 --> 00:46.260
the truth will not bring results. In my own case, I found the easiest way is in casting the burden.

00:47.060 --> 00:51.040
A metaphysician once explained it in this manner. He said,

00:51.520 --> 00:58.260
The only thing which gives anything weight in nature is the law of gravitation. And if a boulder

00:58.260 --> 01:04.400
could be taken high above the planet, there would be no weight in that boulder. And that is what

01:04.400 --> 01:12.680
Jesus Christ meant when he said, My yoke is easy and my burden is light. He had overcome the world

01:13.420 --> 01:19.560
and functioned in the fourth dimensional realm, where there is only perfection, completion, life

01:19.560 --> 01:29.260
and joy. He said, Come to me, all ye that labor and are heavy laden, and I will give you rest.

01:30.300 --> 01:39.180
Take my yoke upon you, for my yoke is easy and my burden is light. We are also told in the 55th

01:39.180 --> 01:46.500
Psalm to cast thy burden upon the Lord. Many passages in the Bible state that the battle

01:46.500 --> 01:55.460
is God's, not man's, and that man is always to stand still and see the salvation of the Lord.

01:56.300 --> 02:02.480
This indicates that the super-conscious mind, or Christ within, is the department which fights

02:02.480 --> 02:10.240
man's battle and relieves him of his burdens. We see, therefore, that man violates law if he

02:10.240 --> 02:17.220
carries a burden, and a burden is an adverse thought or condition, and this thought or condition

02:17.220 --> 02:24.060
has its root in the subconscious. It seems almost impossible to make any headway directing the

02:24.060 --> 02:29.580
subconscious from the conscious or reasoning mind, as the reasoning mind, the intellect,

02:29.580 --> 02:36.080
is limited in its conceptions and filled with doubts and fears. How scientific is it, then,

02:36.080 --> 02:43.280
to cast the burden upon the super-conscious mind, or Christ within, where it is made light or

02:43.280 --> 02:49.200
dissolved into its native nothingness? For example, a woman in urgent need of money

02:49.200 --> 02:54.260
may light upon the Christ within, the super-conscious with the statement,

02:54.260 --> 03:01.320
I cast this burden of lack on the Christ within, and I go free to have plenty.

03:02.820 --> 03:09.680
The belief in lack was her burden, and as she cast it upon the super-conscious with its belief

03:09.680 --> 03:18.580
of plenty, an avalanche of supply was the result. We read, the Christ in you, the hope of glory.

03:20.060 --> 03:26.540
Another example. One of my students had been given a new piano, and there was no room in her

03:26.540 --> 03:32.400
studio for it until she had moved out the old one. She was in a state of perplexity.

03:32.700 --> 03:39.240
She wanted to keep the old piano, but knew of no place to send it. She became desperate,

03:39.600 --> 03:46.780
as the new piano was to be sent immediately, in fact, was on its way, with no place to put it.

03:46.780 --> 03:53.760
She said it came to her to repeat, I cast this burden on the Christ within, and I go free.

03:54.920 --> 04:00.840
A few minutes later, her phone rang, and a woman friend asked if she might rent her old piano,

04:01.240 --> 04:09.060
and it was moved out, a few minutes before the new one arrived. I knew a woman whose burden was

04:09.060 --> 04:15.940
resentment. She said, I cast this burden of resentment on the Christ within, and I go free

04:15.940 --> 04:24.200
to be loving, harmonious, and happy. The Almighty Superconscious flooded the subconscious with love,

04:24.980 --> 04:29.920
and her whole life was changed. For years, resentment had held her in a state of torment

04:29.920 --> 04:36.560
and imprisoned her soul, the subconscious mind. The statement should be made over and over and

04:36.560 --> 04:43.560
over, sometimes for hours at a time, silently or audibly, with quietness, but determination.

04:44.520 --> 04:52.120
I have often compared it to winding up a Victrola. We must wind ourselves up with spoken words.

04:53.080 --> 04:58.740
I have noticed in casting the burden, after a little while, one seems to see clearly.

04:59.500 --> 05:07.120
It is impossible to have clear vision while in the throes of carnal mind. Doubts and fear poison

05:07.120 --> 05:12.840
the mind and body, and imagination runs riot, attracting disaster and disease.

05:13.660 --> 05:20.240
In steadily repeating the affirmation, I cast this burden on the Christ within, and go free.

05:20.900 --> 05:27.440
The vision clears, and with it a feeling of relief, and sooner or later comes the manifestation of

05:27.440 --> 05:34.560
good, be it health, happiness, or supply. One of my students once asked me to explain the

05:34.560 --> 05:40.500
darkness before the dawn. I referred in a preceding chapter to the fact that often,

05:40.860 --> 05:47.280
before the big demonstration, everything seems to go wrong, and deep depression clouds the

05:47.280 --> 05:53.860
consciousness. It means that out of the subconscious are rising the doubts and fears of the ages.

05:54.500 --> 06:01.940
These old derelicts of the subconscious rise to the surface, to be put out. It is then that man

06:01.940 --> 06:09.240
should clap his cymbals, like Jehoshaphat, and give thanks that he is saved, even though he seems

06:09.240 --> 06:15.240
surrounded by the enemy, the situation of lack or disease. The student continued,

06:15.720 --> 06:23.120
How long must one remain in the dark? And I replied, Until one can see in the dark.

06:23.840 --> 06:28.060
And casting the burden enables one to see in the dark.

06:28.920 --> 06:37.360
In order to impress the subconscious, active faith is always essential. Faith without works is dead.

06:38.020 --> 06:41.860
In these chapters, I have endeavored to bring out this point.

06:43.980 --> 06:50.680
Jesus Christ showed active faith when he commanded the multitude to sit down on the ground

06:50.680 --> 06:57.540
before he gave thanks for the loaves and the fishes. I will give another example showing

06:57.540 --> 07:05.760
how necessary this step is. In fact, active faith is the bridge over which man passes to his

07:05.760 --> 07:13.300
promised land. Through misunderstanding, a woman had been separated from her husband, whom she loved

07:13.300 --> 07:20.080
deeply. He refused all offers of reconciliation and would not communicate with her in any way.

07:20.940 --> 07:25.560
Coming into the knowledge of spiritual law, she denied the appearance of separation.

07:25.560 --> 07:32.060
She made this statement, There is no separation in divine mind. Therefore,

07:32.640 --> 07:38.320
I cannot be separated from the love and companionship which are mine by divine right.

07:39.420 --> 07:46.760
She showed active faith by arranging a place for him at the table every day, thereby impressing

07:46.760 --> 07:53.980
the subconscious with a picture of his return. Over a year passed, but she never wavered,

07:53.980 --> 07:56.620
and one day he walked in.

07:58.480 --> 08:05.000
The subconscious is often impressed through music. Music has a fourth-dimensional quality

08:05.000 --> 08:10.920
and releases the soul from imprisonment. It makes wonderful things seem possible,

08:11.320 --> 08:18.000
and easy of accomplishment. I have a friend who uses her Victrola daily for this purpose.

08:18.000 --> 08:25.860
It puts her in perfect harmony and releases the imagination. Another woman often dances while

08:25.860 --> 08:32.620
making her affirmations. The rhythm and harmony of music and motion carry her words forth with

08:32.620 --> 08:40.320
tremendous power. The student must remember also not to despise the day of small things.

08:41.160 --> 08:48.420
Invariably, before a demonstration come signs of land. Before Columbus reached America,

08:48.640 --> 08:56.340
he saw birds and twigs which showed him land was near. So it is with a demonstration, but often the

08:56.340 --> 09:03.060
student mistakes it for the demonstration itself and is disappointed. For example, a woman had

09:03.060 --> 09:09.620
spoken the word for a set of dishes. Not long afterwards, a friend gave her a dish which was

09:09.620 --> 09:16.780
cracked. She came to me and said, well, I asked for a set of dishes and all I got was a cracked

09:16.780 --> 09:24.140
plate. I replied, the plate was only signs of land. It shows your dishes are coming.

09:24.600 --> 09:29.800
Look upon it as birds and seaweed. And not long afterwards, the dishes came.

09:31.120 --> 09:36.780
Continually making believe impresses the subconscious. If one makes believe he is

09:37.400 --> 09:45.260
and makes believe he is successful, in due time he will reap. Children are always making believe

09:45.260 --> 09:53.020
and except ye be converted and become as little children, you shall not enter the kingdom of

09:53.020 --> 10:00.300
heaven. For example, I know of a woman who was very poor, but no one could make her feel poor.

10:00.300 --> 10:06.680
She earned a small amount of money from rich friends who constantly reminded her of her poverty

10:06.680 --> 10:13.480
and to be careful and saving. Regardless of their admonitions, she would spend all her earnings on a

10:13.480 --> 10:20.500
hat or make someone a gift and be in a rapturous state of mind. Her thoughts were always centered

10:20.500 --> 10:28.300
on beautiful clothes and rings and things, but without envying others. She lived in the world of

10:28.300 --> 10:35.600
wondrous and only riches seemed real to her. Before long she married a rich man and the rings

10:35.600 --> 10:43.040
and things became visible. I do not know whether the man was the divine selection, but opulence had

10:43.040 --> 10:51.060
to manifest in her life as she had imaged only opulence. There is no peace or happiness for man

10:51.060 --> 10:58.280
until he has erased all fear from the subconscious. Fear is misdirected energy and must be redirected.

10:58.300 --> 11:06.240
Or transmuted into faith. Jesus Christ said, Why are ye fearful, O ye of little faith?

11:06.840 --> 11:13.640
All things are possible to him that believeth. I am asked so often by my students,

11:14.320 --> 11:20.900
how can I get rid of fear? I replied by walking up to the thing you are afraid of.

11:21.960 --> 11:25.440
The lion takes its fierceness from your fear.

11:27.060 --> 11:33.000
Walk up to the lion and he will disappear. Run away and he runs after you. I have shown

11:33.000 --> 11:38.160
in previous chapters how the lion of lack disappeared when the individual spent money

11:38.160 --> 11:45.200
fearlessly, showing faith that God was his supply and therefore unfailing. Many of my

11:45.200 --> 11:49.740
students have come out of the bondage of poverty and are now bountifully supplied

11:49.740 --> 11:56.820
through losing all fear of letting money go out. The subconscious is impressed with the truth that

11:56.820 --> 12:05.560
God is the giver and the gift. Therefore, as one is one with the giver, he is one with the gift.

12:06.180 --> 12:12.100
A splendid statement is, I now thank God the giver, for God the gift.

12:13.060 --> 12:20.080
Man has so long separated himself from his good and his supply, through thoughts of separation

12:20.080 --> 12:26.600
and lack, that sometimes it takes dynamite to dislodge these false ideas from the subconscious,

12:27.160 --> 12:32.660
and the dynamite is a big situation. We see in the foregoing illustration

12:32.660 --> 12:38.020
how the individual was freed from his bondage by showing fearlessness.

12:39.160 --> 12:45.680
Man should watch himself hourly to detect if his motive for action is fear or faith.

12:46.740 --> 12:55.660
Choose ye this day whom we shall serve, fear or faith. Perhaps one's fear is of personality.

12:56.400 --> 13:03.060
Then, do not avoid the people feared. Be willing to meet them cheerfully and they will either

13:03.700 --> 13:09.380
golden links in the chain of one's good, or disappear harmoniously from one's pathway.

13:10.480 --> 13:17.780
Perhaps one's fear is of disease or germs. Then one should be fearless and undisturbed

13:17.780 --> 13:26.220
in a germ-laden situation, and he would be immune. One can only contract germs while

13:26.220 --> 13:33.660
vibrating at the same rate as the germ, and fear drags men down to the level of the germ.

13:34.300 --> 13:40.580
Of course, the disease-laden germ is the product of carnal mind, as all thought must objectify.

13:41.000 --> 13:46.080
Germs do not exist in the superconscious or divine mind, therefore are the products of

13:46.080 --> 13:53.780
man's vain imagination. In the twinkling of an eye, man's release will come when he realizes

13:53.780 --> 14:01.080
there is no power in evil. The material world will fade away, and the fourth-dimensional world,

14:01.280 --> 14:05.100
the world of the wondrous, will swing into manifestation.

14:06.800 --> 14:14.800
And I saw a new heaven and a new earth, and there shall be no more death, neither sorrow nor crying,

14:15.520 --> 14:21.020
neither shall there be any more pain, for the former things are passed away.

14:23.060 --> 14:27.640
End of chapter 6. Recording by Amy Conger

